commentary: Rahmat Shah to Ahmed Raza, OUT miscues the drive off the half volley, takes the outer half of the bat, short cover Sami dives forward and to his right, takes the ball inches off the ground, umpire Sarika Prasad confers with his colleague Buddhi Pradhan at square leg before raising the finger and Afghanistan have won by 70 runs
